 Kundalini Yoga awakens the Kundalini energy (awakening energy) through yoga poses, breathing exercises, mantras and visualizations.
 The center of Tibetan meditation is the God-Yoga. By visualizing various deities, the energy channels are purified, the chakras are opened and the enlightened consciousness arises.
