 Cancellation policies vary, but by the end of March, most cancellation policies were waived because of the Coronavirus until July 2020, when the Olympics were scheduled to be held.
 It is estimated that most tickets for the event will cost between 2,500 yen and 130,000 yen, with an average ticket costing around 7,000 yen.
